    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Explosive Ghostflame</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" title="Explosive Ghostflame" src="/file/Elden-Ring/explosive_ghostflame_sorcery_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="explosive ghostflame sorcery elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Death Sorceries" href="/Death+Sorceries" target="">Death Sorceries</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost 29</td> 
     <td>Slots Used&nbsp;1</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Causes ghostflame explosion that burns wide area 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Intelligence" href="/Intelligence" target="">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;42 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith" target="">Faith</a>&nbsp;30 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arcane" href="/Arcane" target="">Arcane</a>&nbsp;0 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Explosive Ghostflame</strong> is a&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sorceries" href="/Sorceries" target="">Sorcery</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Explosive Ghostflame spell</strong>&nbsp;causes burning to surrounding area when cast. Updated to&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>Sorcery of the servants of Death.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Strike the ground with the staff, triggering an explosion of ghostflame that burns the surrounding area.</em></p> 
 <p><em>In the time when there was no Erdtree, death was burned in ghostflame. Deathbirds were the keepers of that fire.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Explosive Ghostflame</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Explosive Ghostflame</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Drops from a <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Death Rite Bird" href="/Death+Rite+Bird">Death Rite Bird</a> southeast <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Apostate Derelict" href="/Apostate+Derelict">Apostate Derelict</a> (late game area). It's a clearing in the frozen river, and you must go there at night. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=6371&amp;lat=-60.71094&amp;lng=136.0576&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=6371&amp;lat=-60.71094&amp;lng=136.0576&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Explosive Ghostflame Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Death Sorceries" href="/Death+Sorceries">Death Sorcery</a></li> 
 <li>Can be boosted by&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Prince of Death's Staff" href="/Prince+of+Death's+Staff" target="">Prince of Death's Staff</a></li> 
 <li>Stamina Cost:&nbsp;45</li> 
 <li>Deals magic damage</li> 
 <li>Inflicts Frostbite on opponents. Initial explosion deals&nbsp;130&nbsp;and flames deal 38 per tick</li> 
 <li>When casting, the caster holds their staff in two hands and thrusts it into the ground, generating an explosion and leaving patches of ghostflame on the ground. The initial explosion has good knockback, and the fire may be good for zoning enemy players in PvP, but overall this spell deals weak damage for the FP cost and leaves the caster vulnerable.</li> 
 <li><span style="color: #ff6600;">NOTE</span>: This skill was changed with&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>&nbsp;as follows:&nbsp; 
  <ul> 
   <li>The Frostbite buildup of this spell was significantly increased - the initial explosion frost buildup was increased from 50 to 130 and the lingering ghostflame was increased from 28 frost buildup per tick to 38 per tick.</li> 
   <li>The attack power of the spell has been increased.</li> 
   <li>The stamina damage done to guarding enemies has been increased.</li> 
   <li>The range of the residual ghostflame left after the explosion has been increased.&nbsp;</li> 
   <li>The damage detection time of the lingering ghostflame has been reduced.</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
